Readings: Security Auditing

These articles were about how to choose the best IT Auditing and Cybersecurity Solutions depending on the situation and the needs of that company. The audits will be different depending on the sector of business that they conduct. An audit can provide a company very valuable information about the security controls of a company. Risk management audits force us to be vulnerable and expose all of the systems and strategies that are being conducted by that company. They can make some people uncomfortable but they are actually very valuable with the information that is discovered and can then lead to more protection. 






